data.text:
If Cyfin is not receiving URL data from your SonicWall device, the issue is likely due to configuration settings within SonicWall. To resolve this issue, please refer to the following SonicWall Knowledge Base article, which provides detailed instructions on how to adjust the necessary settings:

SonicWall Knowledge Base Article: No entries under Log | Reports – Unable to see web site hits/information after firmware upgrade

For further assistance, please contact our support team.
